value of $\rho_H = -0.018$ and 0.45 for $\tau_m/\tau_{NL} = 0.5$ and $\infty$, respectively. 

The red and blue colour in Fig. \ref{fig:visualisations} indicate right-hand (positive helicity) and left-hand (negative helicity) circularly polarized helical waves, respectively.

